		(descr "noknok standard mounting hole: M2.5, 2.5mm NPTH, no annular. Adafruit/Qwiic-aligned (M2.5 nylon screw+standoff kit, e.g. Adafruit 3299). Courtyard 2.8mm radius tracks the ~5mm M2.5 head/standoff. Place hole center >= 2.25mm from the board edge (3mm preferred). This is the plain second mounting hole; the other hole on the board is noknok_FlashPads_I2C-module_1x3_M2.5 (same hole geometry + the flashing pads).")
